
## Goal
- Build **one self-contained `index.html`** portfolio site for a film/video student, wired to Supabase for data and file storage.
-O utput must be a single downloadable HTML file. Deploy target: Vercel.
 

## Tech stack
HTML (single file) · Vite · Supabase (Postgres + Storage) · Vercel.

