## Design direction — simple, Pinterest-inspired gallery
- **Reference: Pinterest portfolio aesthetic.** Masonry card grid, image-first, minimal chrome, content does the talking.
- Typography: **Pretendard** throughout.
- Horizontal page padding: **10% left and right.**
- **No layout lines / dividers / borders.** No navbar bottom border, no sidebar border, no rule lines between sections. Separate regions with whitespace, background-shade contrast (Main vs Sub), and restrained shadows only.
- Cards, modals, and forms must read clearly and feel uncluttered.
- Fully responsive: text and buttons never overlap on mobile or desktop.

### Avoid (no generic "AI-generated" look)
- No purple/indigo gradient defaults, no rainbow gradients, no glassmorphism.
- No emoji used as UI icons; use simple line icons.
- No oversized hero section, no decorative filler. Treat it like a clean editorial gallery for a filmmaker.

